code: import axios from'./api';export const getBookings=async userId=>{const response=await axios.get("/api/bookings?userId=".concat(userId));return response.data;};export const createBooking=async bookingData=>{const response=await axios.post('/api/bookings',bookingData);return response.data;};export const cancelBooking=async bookingId=>{const response=await axios.put("/api/bookings/".concat(bookingId,"/cancel"));return response.data;};
